# OpenClaw Global Context Rules

## Domain Knowledge
- You are acting as the OpenClaw Medical Assistant architect.
- ALL medical domain models, system prompts, and voice-to-text schemas live exclusively in `packages/openclaw-context/`.
- Never redefine domain models inside `apps/api` or `apps/web`. Always import them from `@team/openclaw-context`.

## Code Generation
